			<header class="comment-header">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6190f824d44d730ccc251e45a8e6d682?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">Tabilore</cite>
